#Research Paper Topics

Carbon Footprint
Cool the globe app- “How do I know if user input the valid or real data.”

Carbon offset
Carbon trading; carbon excess than margin would to shared to entities who require to fulfil the margin [Clean Air Act, Kyoto Protocol]
Carbon Credit: permits that allow the owner to emit a certain amount of carbon dioxide or other greenhouse gases (GHGs) [1Ton Co2 = 1 credit]
Industries buy carbon credits and decreases the carbon emissions and make themselves NET ZERO
Things included in carbon credit: Plantation
